				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hbox {CO}_{2}$$\end{document} equivalent within the European Union Emission Trading Scheme by July 2019 (Kárászová et al. 2020). This value of carbon allowance started at $5.17/tonne CO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
