Absorption is a technique of transporting the matters from their vapour state to the fluid phase as long as that the vapour is dissolvable in that fluid (Abdeen et al. 2016). In the state of CO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
