				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hbox {N}_{2}$$\end{document} atmosphere. The presence of CO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
